node.title: How a push to address vaccine hesitancy in pregnant women is gaining ground
node.description: A group of medical researchers is closing the gap on COVID-19 vaccination among pregnant women, after collating resources on how to discuss the vaccine and frequently-asked questions tailored for pregnant women.

node.title: Spotify bows to Adele, drops 'shuffle' as album default setting
node.description: The world's largest streaming service will finally allow subscribers to listen to an album's tracks in the order the artist intended, after musicians like Adele campaigned for the change.

node.title: Homicide investigation underway after man, 22, dies in Auckland
node.description: The man was dropped off at a Takanini medical centre about 12.45pm with critical injuries and was taken to Middlemore Hospital where he died shortly after.
